Package: classecol
Title: Ecological text classifiers
Version: 0.4
Authors@R: person("Thomas Frederick", "Johnson", email = "thomas.frederick.johnson@outlook.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Text classifiers for nature culturomics. This includes functions to clean text data. Models built of twitter data but could be used for any text written by the general public. Current classifiers fall into three domains: Hunting, Wildlife, Biography
License: creative commons
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
